No. 619. National Salt Company, Petitioner, v. George S. Ingraham. March. 19, 1906. Mr. Maxwell Evarts and Mr. Henry B. Twombly for petitioner. Mr. George S. Ingraham pro se.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the *645Second. Circuit-denied.
